# Planner — Pathwaize Intelligence Center Demo (FINAL — all research resolved)

## Status: READY — no open unknowns

All critical blockers from plan-gate.out resolved by pre-researcher. Plan is complete and ready for demo-builder.

---

## Demo Concept

**Pathwaize Intelligence Center** — a self-contained, browser-side AI workflow execution console. Three AI engines (Authority, Newsletter, Knowledge Lite) wired end-to-end through a strict Run → Generate → Review → Revise → Approve → Push pipeline. WebGPU local inference via WebLLM (no exposed API keys). IndexedDB persistence. Mock GHL chrome wrapper simulates iframe embed context.

**Prototype vs Full: FULL**
Feature richness 10 requires all 3 engines functional, full approval-gate state machine, run records, usage/cost log, Intel Brief stub, prompt chips, persistent intelligence input, output queue, workspace context. No scope item trips the prototype fallback rules.

**Backend blueprint: NOT needed.** In-browser LLMRouter mirrors the production backend contract exactly. Save/push simulated with realistic receipts. No mw-backend change required.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Choice |
|---|---|
| LLM runtime | `@mlc-ai/web-llm` from CDN (WebWorker offload, JSON schema enforcement built in) |
| Primary model | `Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct-q4f16_1-MLC` (~4–5GB VRAM, richness-10 generation quality) |
| Router model | `Qwen2.5-1.5B-Instruct-q4f16_1-MLC` (intent classification + JSON validation) |
| VRAM fallback | `Qwen2.5-3B-Instruct-q4f16_1-MLC` (auto-switch if adapter VRAM < 5GB) |
| Storage | IndexedDB native (runs, outputs, logs, workspace) |
| Frontend | Vanilla JS + ES modules, no bundler, no build step |
| Hosting | `public/demos/real-estate-intelligence-center/` — same-origin static, auto-deploys with site |

