```
[ Your context: Austin fix-and-flip investor | Lead source: cold calls | Tone: direct ]  [Edit]
```
Stored in IndexedDB `workspace` table. Injected as system prompt prefix on every engine call. Editable via modal; changes persist to IndexedDB immediately.

