## Prompt Chips

Horizontal chip row below persistent intelligence bar:
```
[Generate LinkedIn Post]  [Write Newsletter]  [Document Process]  [Brainstorm Topics]  [Research Comp]
```
Click → auto-selects correct engine tab + pre-fills run input form with smart defaults.

