| Approval gating (no auto-push) | app.js | Push disabled until status === approved |
| Google Drive + GitHub picker | engines/knowledge.js, mock-integrations.js | Picker UI + mock receipt |
| Run records visible | db.js, ui/shell.js | History bar: timestamp / engine / model / cost / status |
| Output status tracking | db.js, ui/output-queue.js | 6-state colored chips everywhere |
| Usage/cost logging | db.js, ui/shell.js | Per-run cost + aggregate bottom panel |
| Error handling | llm-router.js, app.js | Inline error cards; 1-retry reflection; graceful error state |
| Workspace/subaccount indicator | ui/shell.js | Workspace name + context in header |
| Bespoke design | styles.css, index.html | Dark execution console, Inter + DM Mono, palette above |
| WebGPU fallback | llm-router.js | Mock-LLM mode if no WebGPU; VRAM auto-fallback to 3B |
| No em/en dashes | All files | Hard enforced in all copy and generated demo text |

