## Build Priority Order (for demo-builder)

1. `index.html` + `styles.css` — 3-col shell, GHL wrapper, font/CDN imports, CSS token declarations
2. `db.js` — IndexedDB init, all 4 stores, CRUD helpers
3. `llm-router.js` — WebLLM dual-model init, VRAM detection, mock-LLM fallback (P0: progress bar UI), `.run()` contract, JSON validation + 1-retry reflection
4. `app.js` — engine dispatcher, status machine, event bus, prompt chip handlers
5. `engines/authority.js` — step 1 of full engine pipeline (Priority 1 per brief)
6. `engines/newsletter.js` — subject-line selectable cards (Priority 2)
7. `engines/knowledge.js` — destination picker (Priority 3)
8. `mock-integrations.js` — Drive/GitHub/LinkedIn/X receipts
9. `ui/shell.js` — persistent intelligence bar, usage panel, run history bar
10. `ui/output-queue.js` — pending review list
11. `ui/intel-brief.js` — 6-section stub
12. QA pass: all 17 traceability gates, no console errors, no em/en dashes

